    <h1>Moment Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">Creating real-time content tied to a live event, trending topic, or cultural moment. The brands that do it well earn <strong>organic reach that paid campaigns can't buy</strong> — and the ones that miss it hand that reach to competitors.</p>
